DOMAIN-SUFFIX,login.live.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,msauth.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,msauthimages.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,msftauth.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,msftauthimages.net

# --- Windows Copilot / Copilot App ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,windowscopilot.microsoft.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,widgets.microsoft.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,services.windows.com

# --- 其他可能的 Copilot 相关域名（补充） ---
